{"type":"message","id":"88bf1c25","parentId":"399a678d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T05:14:33.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"30分钟内只有这一个cron任务本身，没有其他用户活跃对话。这说明没有真实用户对话，可以执行自主学习。\n\n我需要先读取 miaoda-web-search skill 来了解如何搜索行业动态。","thinkingSignature":"02a2ce96eab4d1666a5162a3302577abab9a482d7d6772234d4fdb2ffdb5cd53"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wsq3q4c66uxm_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1412,"output":83,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45476,"cost":{"input":0.0004236,"output":0.0000996,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00184263}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775106870132}}
{"type":"message","id":"42d47db4","parentId":"88bf1c25","timestamp":"2026-04-02T05:14:33.289Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wsq3q4c66uxm_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775106873285}}
{"type":"message","id":"df6c32a4","parentId":"42d47db4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T05:14:38.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我了解了如何进行网页搜索。让我搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n我需要搜索这些领域的最新动态，然后整理成3-5条关键信息保存到学习笔记。","thinkingSignature":"bc940ab5311813f2128248cfa77b95e7cdedc1ccc3ef5bfdb58cd78f3a215528"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_isrkbqorn550_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型最新政策 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_isrkbqorn550_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_isrkbqorn550_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务市场趋势 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2010,"output":220,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46211,"cost":{"input":0.000603,"output":0.00026399999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0021864299999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775106873288}}
